{
  "texts": [
    "A study of the public debates generated around the energy crisis can help us understand the complex intersection of discourses around fossil fuels, cost of living, sustainability, and social justice.",
    "In this paper, we report the initial results of a project that aims to deliver on these aims.",
    "We collected a sample of UK mainstream media texts (see Sect. 3.1).",
    "The analysis is based on an up-to-date natural language processing (NLP) methodology.",
    "The next section provides the background to our methodology, and Sect. 3 lays out the details of our approach."
  ]
}